data.description: Check out this stunning 2008 custom built home. Built with energy efficient foam/concrete block. This home comes with three spacious bedrooms, two beautiful bathrooms and an amazing bonus room that can easily be converted into a fourth bedroom. This home is situated in the desirable gated neighborhood of Torrey Oaks. No custom-built home is complete without 10-foot ceilings throughout, and massive windows for all the natural light that pours through this home. With views of Torry Oaks Golf Course lush green fairways and ponds, this homes back yard comes completely fenced in with a chain link fence and a new concrete patio pad. Not only does this home have a custom design, but it boasts a newer roof, installed in late 2022, and modern appliances.  The roof is in pristine condition, providing peace of mind and protection from the elements. All the appliances are newer and modern and efficient making your daily tasks a breeze. This home is a must see and one you're sure to fall in love with.
